{
  "text": "We can see that the efficiency of the proposed algorithm is greater than Li and Kang 7 and Malik et al. [CITATION_1] and lower than Mertens et al. [CITATION_2] Because only the luminance component Y is fused in the wavelet domain, that the computing time of the proposed algorithm is much smaller than Malik et al., [CITATION_3] which fuses all channels of the lab color space in the wavelet domain. We can also find that the computing time of the proposed algorithm is almost proportional to the size of input images from Table 5 . The computationally ",
